Interface BusinessObjectIdentifierFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusinessObjectIdentifierFactoryImpl

    public interface BusinessObjectIdentifierFactory
    Provides factory methods to create a BusinessObjectIdentifier.
    Since:
    6.0

    • Method Detail

      • createBusinessObjectType

        BusinessObjectType createBusinessObjectType(java.lang.String typeStr)
        Creates the business object type object from the parameter passed and returns its instance. This method should be used to create a business object type having same type identifier and type name.
        Parameters:
        typeStr - Contains business object type.
        Returns:
        Business object type.

      • createBusinessObjectType

        BusinessObjectType createBusinessObjectType(java.lang.String typeStr,
                                            java.lang.String nameStr)
        Creates the business object type object from the parameters passed and returns its instance. This method should be used to create a business object type having different type identifier and type name.
        Parameters:
        typeStr - Contains business object type.
        nameStr - Contains the human readable business object type name.
        Returns:
        Business object type.

      • createBusinessObjectKey

        BusinessObjectKey createBusinessObjectKey(java.lang.String keyStr)
        Creates the business object key object from the parameter passed and returns its instance.
        Parameters:
        keyStr - Contains uniquely identifiable key of the business object.
        Returns:
        Business object key.

      • createBusinessObjectIdentifier

        BusinessObjectIdentifier createBusinessObjectIdentifier(BusinessObjectType type,
                                                        BusinessObjectKey key)
        Creates business object identifier for specified business object type identifier and business object key.
        Parameters:
        type - Contains business object type.
        key - Contains key used by business object modules to uniquely identify an instance of a business object of a particular type.
        Returns:
        An instance of business object identifier.

      • createBusinessObjectIdentifier

        BusinessObjectIdentifier createBusinessObjectIdentifier(java.lang.String typeStr,
                                                        java.lang.String keyStr)
        Creates business object identifier for specified business object type identifier and business object key.
        Parameters:
        typeStr - Contains business object type.
        keyStr - Contains key used by business object modules to uniquely identify an instance of a business object of a particular type.
        Returns:
        An instance of business object identifier.
